<types> <xs:schema attributeFormDefault="unqualified" elementFormDefault="qualified" targetNamespace="http://example.com/notify/"> <xs:element name="notify" type="xs:string"/> </xs:schema>
<xs:schema attributeFormDefault="unqualified" elementFormDefault="qualified" targetNamespace="http://example.com/echo/"> <xs:element name="echoIn" type="xs:string"/> <xs:element name="echoOut" type="xs:string"/> </xs:schema> </types>
<message name="wsaNotifyMessage"> <part element="s0:notify" name="wsaNotifyMessagePart"/> </message>
<message name="wsaEchoInMessage"> <part element="s1:echoIn" name="wsaEchoInPart"/> </message>
<message name="wsaEchoOutMessage"> <part element="s1:echoOut" name="wsaEchoOutPart"/> </message>
<portType name="wsaTestPortType"> <operation name="notify"> <input message="service:wsaNotifyMessage"/> </operation>
<operation name="echoIn"> <input message="service:wsaEchoInMessage"/> </operation>
<operation name="echoOut"> <input message="service:wsaEchoOutMessage"/> </operation>
<operation name="echo"> <input message="service:wsaEchoInMessage"/> <output message="service:wsaEchoOutMessage"/> </operation> </portType>
<binding name="wsaTestSoap11Binding" type="service:wsaTestPortType"> <soap:binding style="document" transport="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/http"/> <operation name="notify"> <soap:operation soapAction="" style="document"/> <input> <soap:body use="literal"/> </input> </operation>
<operation name="echoIn"> <soap:operation soapAction="" style="document"/> <input> <soap:body use="literal"/> </input> </operation>
<operation name="echoOut"> <soap:operation soapAction="" style="document"/> <input> <soap:body use="literal"/> </input> </operation>
<operation name="echo"> <soap:operation soapAction="" style="document"/> <input> <soap:body use="literal"/> </input> <output> <soap:body use="literal"/> </output> </operation>
</binding>
<service name="wsaTestService"> <port binding="service:wsaTestSoap11Binding" name="wsaTestPort"> <soap:address location="http://example.com/node/B"/> </port> </service> </definitions><description targetNamespace="http://example.com/wsaTestService" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2006/01/wsdl" xmlns:echo="http://example.com/echo/" xmlns:notify="http://example.com/notify/" xmlns:service="http://example.com/wsaTestService" xmlns:whttp="http://www.w3.org/2006/01/wsdl/http" xmlns:wsdlx="http://www.w3.org/2006/01/wsdl-extensions" xmlns:wsoap="http://www.w3.org/2006/01/wsdl/soap" xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">
<types> <xs:schema attributeFormDefault="unqualified" elementFormDefault="qualified" targetNamespace="http://example.com/notify/"> <xs:element name="notify" type="xs:string"/> </xs:schema> <xs:schema attributeFormDefault="unqualified" elementFormDefault="qualified" targetNamespace="http://example.com/echo/"> <xs:element name="echoIn" type="xs:string"/> <xs:element name="echoOut" type="xs:string"/> </xs:schema> </types>
<interface name="wsaTestService"> <fault name="service:EmptyEchoString"/> <operation name="notify" pattern="http://www.w3.org/2005/08/wsdl/in-only"> <input element="notify:notify" messageLabel="In"/> </operation> <operation name="echoIn" pattern="http://www.w3.org/2005/08/wsdl/robust-in-only"> <input element="s1:echoIn" messageLabel="In"/> <outfault messageLabel="Out" ref="service:EmptyEchoString"/> </operation> <operation name="echoOut" pattern="http://www.w3.org/2005/08/wsdl/robust-in-only"> <input element="s1:echoOut" messageLabel="In"/> <outfault messageLabel="Out" ref="service:EmptyEchoString"/> </operation> <operation name="echo" pattern="http://www.w3.org/2005/08/wsdl/in-out"> <input element="s1:echoIn" messageLabel="In"/> <output element="s1:echoOut" messageLabel="Out"/> <outfault messageLabel="Out" ref="service:EmptyEchoString"/> </operation> </interface>
<binding interface="wsaTestService" name="wsaTestSoap11Binding" type="http://www.w3.org/2005/08/wsdl/soap" wsoap:version="1.1"> wsoap:protocol="http://www.w3.org/2003/05/soap/bindings/HTTP"> <operation ref="notify"/> <operation ref="echoIn"/> <operation ref="echoOut"/> <operation ref="echo"/> <fault ref="service:EmptyEchoString" wsoap:code="echo:EmptyEchoString"/> </binding>
<binding interface="wsaTestService" name="wsaTestSoap12Binding" type="http://www.w3.org/2005/08/wsdl/soap" wsoap:version="1.2"> wsoap:protocol="http://www.w3.org/2003/05/soap/bindings/HTTP"> <!-- Note: the request only SOAP MEP doesn't actually exist! --> <operation ref="notify" wsoap:mep="http://www.w3.org/2003/05/soap/mep/request"/> <operation ref="echoIn" wsoap:mep="http://www.w3.org/2003/05/soap/mep/request"/> <operation ref="echoOut" wsoap:mep="http://www.w3.org/2003/05/soap/mep/request"/> <operation ref="echo" wsoap:mep="http://www.w3.org/2003/05/soap/mep/request-response"/> <fault ref="service:EmptyEchoString" wsoap:code="echo:EmptyEchoString"/> </binding>
<service interface="service:wsaTestService" name="wsaTestService"> <endpoint address="http://example.com/node/B" binding="service:wsaTestSoap11Binding" name="wsaTestSoap11Endpoint"/> <endpoint address="http://example.com/node/B" binding="service:wsaTestSoap12Binding" name="wsaTestSoap12Endpoint"/> </service>
</description></wsa:Metadata></wsa:ReplyTo></soapenv:Header><soapenv:Body><m:notify xmlns:m="http://example.org/notify">test1107</m:notify></soapenv:Body></soapenv:Envelope>
